{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/argocd-slack","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.36363636363637%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"head\"\n        title=\"head\"\n        src=\"/static/2b4c2d7f0e9583812cce740bf10625cc/7c811/head.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2b4c2d7f0e9583812cce740bf10625cc/103f2/head.png 165w,\n/static/2b4c2d7f0e9583812cce740bf10625cc/748ba/head.png 330w,\n/static/2b4c2d7f0e9583812cce740bf10625cc/7c811/head.png 660w,\n/static/2b4c2d7f0e9583812cce740bf10625cc/d28e0/head.png 990w,\n/static/2b4c2d7f0e9583812cce740bf10625cc/a4588/head.png 1254w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"들어가며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"들어가며 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>들어가며</h2>\n<p>사내에서 배포 자동화로 ArgoCD를 사용하고 있는데, 여러 개발자가 Sync를 맞추는 작업을 할때에 동시에 작업을 수행할 수도 있는 우려가 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>그래서 누군가 Sync를 맞추는 작업을 할때나 완료되었을때, 실패하였을때, 파드가 죽었을 때 슬랙을 통해 알림을 보내는 설정을 하였습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-setting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-setting\" aria-label=\"how to setting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How To Setting</h2>\n<h3 id=\"slack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#slack\" aria-label=\"slack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Slack</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.9090909090909%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/bbbe853f90fcd7f3ee28ebd711a1e45a/7c811/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bbbe853f90fcd7f3ee28ebd711a1e45a/103f2/1.png 165w,\n/static/bbbe853f90fcd7f3ee28ebd711a1e45a/748ba/1.png 330w,\n/static/bbbe853f90fcd7f3ee28ebd711a1e45a/7c811/1.png 660w,\n/static/bbbe853f90fcd7f3ee28ebd711a1e45a/d28e0/1.png 990w,\n/static/bbbe853f90fcd7f3ee28ebd711a1e45a/41314/1.png 1074w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>먼저 Slack에서 새로운 앱을 만듭니다.</p>\n<p>Create an App > From scratch 버튼을 눌러 애플리케이션을 만들 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 121.21212121212122%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/7c811/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/103f2/2.png 165w,\n/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/748ba/2.png 330w,\n/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/7c811/2.png 660w,\n/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/d28e0/2.png 990w,\n/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/bb51b/2.png 1320w,\n/static/d00d721e2b7bc0ee418c06ca54aab455/825a4/2.png 1972w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>생성한 후 왼쪽 메뉴의 OAuth &#x26; Permissions 메뉴에 접근합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.51515151515152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/794a37ffd26c911c7d64ac4f16d10263/7c811/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/794a37ffd26c911c7d64ac4f16d10263/103f2/3.png 165w,\n/static/794a37ffd26c911c7d64ac4f16d10263/748ba/3.png 330w,\n/static/794a37ffd26c911c7d64ac4f16d10263/7c811/3.png 660w,\n/static/794a37ffd26c911c7d64ac4f16d10263/d28e0/3.png 990w,\n/static/794a37ffd26c911c7d64ac4f16d10263/b4bc2/3.png 1310w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Scopes > Bot Token Scopes에서 chat:writ 기능을 활성화합니다.</p>\n<p>그 후 상단으로 이동하여 Install To Workspace 을 진행합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.45454545454545%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/7c811/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/103f2/4.png 165w,\n/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/748ba/4.png 330w,\n/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/7c811/4.png 660w,\n/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/d28e0/4.png 990w,\n/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/bb51b/4.png 1320w,\n/static/a919a1a38f9bff0aeb4c07453fe6b9dd/f28c3/4.png 1424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>그러면 위와 같이 Bot User OAuth Token 이 발급되게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96.36363636363636%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/f732c56cd64985e2d5f8bba995d13e99/7c811/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f732c56cd64985e2d5f8bba995d13e99/103f2/5.png 165w,\n/static/f732c56cd64985e2d5f8bba995d13e99/748ba/5.png 330w,\n/static/f732c56cd64985e2d5f8bba995d13e99/7c811/5.png 660w,\n/static/f732c56cd64985e2d5f8bba995d13e99/d28e0/5.png 990w,\n/static/f732c56cd64985e2d5f8bba995d13e99/70841/5.png 1094w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>그 후 슬랙에서 해당 앱을 추가해줍니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"argocd\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#argocd\" aria-label=\"argocd permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ArgoCD</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[ ]</code> 으로 되어있는 칸은 직접 입력해야하는 값입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kubectl apply <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-f</span> https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj-labs/argocd-notifications/release-1.0/manifests/install.yaml <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-n</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>argoCD namespace<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n$ kubectl apply <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-f</span> https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj-labs/argocd-notifications/release-1.0/catalog/install.yaml <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-n</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>argoCD namespace<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 명령어를 실행 시켜 ArgoCD Notification의 manifests 파일과 catalog 파일을 적용합니다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"argocd-notifications-secret\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#argocd-notifications-secret\" aria-label=\"argocd notifications secret permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>argocd-notifications-secret</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">apiVersion: v1 \nkind: Secret \nmetadata: \n  name: argocd-notifications-secret \nstringData:\n  slack-token: <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Bot User OAu